CondensedMatterPhysics,2020,Vol.23,No3,33701:1 –11 DOI:10.5488/CMP.23.33701 http://www.icmp.lviv.ua/journal Totalenergycalculationforthemetallichcpphaseof Zninthebulk,layered,andquantumdotlimits D.Olguín∗ CentrodeInvestigaciónydeEstudiosAvanzadosdelInstitutoPolitécnicoNacional –UnidadQuerétaro, LibramientoNorponienteNo.2000,Fracc.RealdeJuriquilla76230,SantiagodeQuerétaro,Querétaro,México ReceivedNovember12,2020,in /uniFB01nalformFebruary12,2020 ThestructuralandelectronicpropertiesofthemetallichcpphaseofZninthebulk,monolayer,bilayer,and quantumdotlimitshavebeenstudiedbyusingtotalenergycalculations.Fromourcalculateddensityofstates andelectronicbandstructure,inagreementwithpreviouswork,bulkhybridizationoftheZn –4s,3p,and 3d orbitalsisobtained.Furthermore,wefoundthatthisorbitalhybridizationisalsoobtainedforthemonolayer, bilayer,andquantumdotsystems.Atthesametime,wefoundthattheZnmonolayerandbilayersystemsshow electronicpropertiescharacteristicoflamellarsystems,whilethequantumdotsystemshowsthebehavior predictedfora0Dsystem.
